@startuml activity_zakat_calculation
' Activity Diagram - Zakat Calculation Workflow
' Purpose: Shows the business workflow for performing a zakat calculation from
' start (or resume draft) through adding/linking items, recalculating, and finalizing.
' Focus on decisions and control flow. Suitable for academic software engineering documentation.

title Activity Diagram - Zakat Calculation

start

:Open Zakat calculation screen;

if (Draft calculation exists?) then (yes)
  :Resume existing draft;
else (no)
  :Start new calculation;
  :Create DRAFT ZakatCalculation;
  :Auto-link unlinked financial items to calculation;
endif

:Apply rules (RuleEngine);
:Compute zakat base and zakat amount;
:Display calculation summary;

repeat
  :Add, link, or remove items;
  :Recalculate;
  :Apply rules and update zakat base / zakat amount;
  :Display updated summary;
repeat while (User makes more changes?) is (yes) not (no)

:User chooses to finalize;

:Set status = FINALIZED;
:Set calculation_date = now;
:Persist calculation (read-only);

:Show finalized result;

stop

@enduml
